<div class="wrapper">

    <h1>Slack Configuration</h1>
    <P>
        These values are controlled through the application's environment.
    </P>

    {{#if slack_config.botToken}}
        <p>This Botkit instance is configured to operate with a single Slack team.</p>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if slack_config.clientId}} 
        <p>
            This Botkit instance is configured to operate with multiple Slack teams 
            using Oauth.
        </p>

        <a href="{{install_link}}">Install Link</a>
    {{/if}}

    <p>
        Make sure these values match the settings <a href="https://api.slack.com/">displayed on the Slack API portal.</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>
        <label>Your receive endpoint URL is:</label>
        <input type="text" readonly value="{{protocol}}://{{host}}{{{botkit_config.webhook_uri}}}">
    </p>



</div>